      "item": {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "def2b2e2a6420bd2",
        "text": "Of course many other network analysis and visualization tools are potentially available, based upon the fact that Neo4j, a \"property graph data base\" is the underlying data base. "
      },
      "date": 1594315239321
